{"title":"Stream your favorite content during road trips with this $100 iOS and Android-compatible adapter","link":"https://www.macworld.com/article/2333399/stream-your-favorite-content-during-road-trips-with-this-100-ios-and-android-compatible-adapter.html","date":1715760000000,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.macworld.com\">Macworld</a></p>\n\n<div>\n<section><div></div></section>\n\n\n\n<p>If you’re tired of hearing your kids ask, “Are we there yet?” during road trips or simply want to outfit your car with streaming abilities, this wireless adapter opens a world of entertainment.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Now only $99.99 (reg. $149), this plug-and-play and <a href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=111346X1569486&amp;url=https://shop.macworld.com/sales/carplay-android-auto-wireless-adapter-with-streaming-app-support?utm_source=macworld.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=carplay-android-auto-wireless-adapter-with-streaming-app-support&amp;utm_term=scsf-596747&amp;utm_content=a0xRn000001AIfpIAG&amp;scsonar=1&amp;xcust=1-1-2333399-1-0-0&amp;sref=https://www.macworld.com/feed\" target=\"_blank\">iOS and Android-compatible adapter allows your passengers to watch content</a> from an array of popular social media and streaming apps.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><div>\n\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This nifty device is like having a <a href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=111346X1569486&amp;url=https://shop.macworld.com/sales/carplay-android-auto-wireless-adapter-with-streaming-app-support?utm_source=macworld.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=carplay-android-auto-wireless-adapter-with-streaming-app-support&amp;utm_term=scsf-596747&amp;utm_content=a0xRn000001AIfpIAG&amp;scsonar=1&amp;xcust=1-1-2333399-1-0-0&amp;sref=https://www.macworld.com/feed\" target=\"_blank\">Roku player in your car</a>, and it’s compatible with over 800 car models going back to 2016 (though it’s not usable for vehicles with wireless CarPlay). Simply plug it in, and passengers can immediately watch their favorite content from apps like TikTok, YouTube, Netflix, Disney+, and more.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The adapter itself is powered by Qualcomm QCM2290 and boasts 16GB of storage, dual Bluetooth technology, WiFi 2.4G and 5G, Android 11.0, and TF card support. It even comes with the following cables and connections:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>USB-A to USB-C Cable</li>\n\n\n\n<li>USB-C to USB-C Cable</li>\n\n\n\n<li>USB-A to USB-A Tee Cable</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Make long (and short!) car rides more enjoyable for your riders with this <a href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=111346X1569486&amp;url=https://shop.macworld.com/sales/carplay-android-auto-wireless-adapter-with-streaming-app-support?utm_source=macworld.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=carplay-android-auto-wireless-adapter-with-streaming-app-support&amp;utm_term=scsf-596747&amp;utm_content=a0xRn000001AIfpIAG&amp;scsonar=1&amp;xcust=1-1-2333399-1-0-0&amp;sref=https://www.macworld.com/feed\" target=\"_blank\">Apple and Android-compatible wireless adapter, now just $99.99</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=111346X1569486&amp;url=https://shop.macworld.com/sales/carplay-android-auto-wireless-adapter-with-streaming-app-support?utm_source=macworld.com&amp;utm_medium=referral-cta&amp;utm_campaign=carplay-android-auto-wireless-adapter-with-streaming-app-support&amp;utm_term=scsf-596747&amp;utm_content=a0xRn000001AIfpIAG&amp;scsonar=1&amp;xcust=1-1-2333399-1-0-0&amp;sref=https://www.macworld.com/feed\" target=\"_blank\"> </a></p>\n\n\n<div><figure><img src=\"https://cdnp0.stackassets.com/fde34b7dbb38874ec56de7fa7254dabe0f152260/store/bf90ade06a486e5181708a8ec324133e7ebc8f1042585905c8819f78c53c/image_processing20240429-17-1hj6xb3.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figure><img loading=\"lazy\" /></figure></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figure><img loading=\"lazy\" /></figure></div>\n</div>\n\t\t